'''賓得士 K-S2'''（'''Pentax K-S2'''）是由[[理光|理光]]於2015年2月9日發表的可全天候拍攝的[[數位單眼相機|數位單眼相機]]。該相機是[[賓得士|賓得士]]的第一款帶有翻轉LCD螢幕的數位單眼相機，推出時也是可全天候拍攝的數位單眼相機中體積最小的<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imaging-resource.com/news/2015/02/09/pentax-k-s2-targets-the-family-photographer-with-handy-mix-of-enthusiast-co |title=Pentax K-S2 targets the family photographer with handy mix of enthusiast, consumer-grade features |author=Mike Tomkins |date={{date|2015-02-09}} |website=imaging-resource.com |access-date={{date|2015-03-19}} |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022040119/https://www.imaging-resource.com/news/2015/02/09/pentax-k-s2-targets-the-family-photographer-with-handy-mix-of-enthusiast-co |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

K-S2發表的同時，理光也發表了與K-S2一起販售的新款可伸縮套裝鏡頭SMC Pentax-DA L 18-50mm f/4-5.6 DC WR RE<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pentaxforums.com/articles/pentax-news/hd-pentax-da-18-50mm-dc-wr-re-announced.html?src=hs |title=HD Pentax-DA 18-50mm DC WR RE Lens Announced |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date={{date|2015-02-09}} |website=pentaxforums.com |access-date={{date|2015-03-19}} |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207185925/https://www.pentaxforums.com/articles/pentax-news/hd-pentax-da-18-50mm-dc-wr-re-announced.html?src=hs |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dpreview.com/articles/3468767489/collapsible-pentax-da-18-50mm-f4-5-6-dc-wr-re-claims-title-of-world-s-shortest-zoom |title=Collapsible Pentax-DA 18-50mm F4-5.6 DC WR RE claims title of world's shortest zoom |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date={{date|2015-02-09}} |website=[[dpreview|dpreview]] |access-date={{date|2015-03-19}} |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303021202/https://www.dpreview.com/articles/3468767489/collapsible-pentax-da-18-50mm-f4-5-6-dc-wr-re-claims-title-of-world-s-shortest-zoom |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這是賓得士自{{link-en|賓得士 DA 18-135mm 鏡頭|Pentax DA 18-135mm lens|18-135mm鏡頭}}以後推出的第二款帶有寧靜對焦馬達的套裝鏡頭。

==獲得獎項==
宾得 K-S2獲得[[影像技術媒體協會|影像技術媒體協會]]（TIPA）2015年最佳高階數位單眼相機獎（Best Digital SLR Advanced）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tipa.com/english/XXV_tipa_awards_2015.html |title=XXV TIPA AWARDS (2015) |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2015 |website=tipa.com |publisher=[[影像技術媒體協會|Technical Image Press Association]] |access-date={{date|2015-04-14}} |archive-date=2021-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202124615/https://www.tipa.com/english/XXV_tipa_awards_2015.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

